This project was a joint work between Ashwin Dandekar, John McCrone, and Shaoyi Han

Build Essentials
1) Install the following libraries:
   a) mesa-common-dev
   b) libgl1-mesa-dev
   c) libglu1-mesa-dev
   d) qt4-default
   e) qt5-default
   f) qtmultimedia5-dev
2) Remove the following library due to a known bug which does not display menus on current versions of Ubuntu (https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/appmenu-qt5/+bug/1307619):
   a) appmenu-qt5
3) Execute the following commands:
   a) qmake -qt=qt5 -makefile -o Makefile CheckersMaster.pro
   b) make
   c) ./CheckersMaster

